&lt;p&gt;Security sources said that an unmanned aerial vehicle (UAV) fell on a house in Chaklala area of Rawalpindi early Tuesday morning.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;They said that no loss of life was reported in the incident. However, they said that the house had sustained some damage.&lt;/p&gt;
